7/28/16 (The Optimist) : 100ft down the side trail you see a shallow, trickling stream cross the trail - hard to collect here. Just below this stream on the right is a black hose but water is only dripping from the hose. If you keep going down to the campsite, walk to the right just below the campsite for the best spot to collect, but even here it's pretty shallow and you may need a scoop
